extends IMetaioWorldPOIManagerDelegate
implements android.media.MediaPlayer.OnCompletionListener, android.media.MediaPlayer.OnPreparedListener, android.media.MediaPlayer.OnErrorListener, android.media.MediaPlayer.OnInfoListener

Class that provides default functionality for some AREL and media callbacks. Override it to provide custom functionality
